-- Euro Extends Decline Against Dollar After Moody's Downgrades Portugal Debt
-- Matthew Brown
-- 2010-07-13T07:29:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/euro-extends-drop-versus-dollar-as-moody-s-downgrades-portugal.html

          
          
             The euro extended its decline
against the dollar after Moody’s Investors Service cut the
rating on Portugal’s government bonds to A1 from Aa2.  
 The euro fell 0.5 percent to $1.2536 as of 8:29 a.m. in
London.  
